  [1] This is different from Digital World Acquisition Corp., the special p=
urpose acquisition company that has a deal to buy Donald Trump=E2=80=99s so=
cial media company and   can=E2=80=99t get the votes to extend the deadline=
 to complete that deal, for a couple of reasons. The main one is probably t=
hat Twitter is owned by index funds, merger arbitrageurs and other institut=
